data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This fully remodeled gem offers modern farmhouse charm, open concept living room/kitchen/dining, additional living/entertainment room in basement, new waterproof LVP flooring on main and in basement, new carpet in main floor bdrms, custom slow-close cabinets and butcher block in kitchen, new lighting and fresh paint throughout. 4 bdrms; 2 full bthrms. Only 3 blocks away from the iconic Indianapolis Motor Speedway! Enjoy the thrill of race day excitement right in your neighborhood with views of the Pagoda from your large, fully fenced backyard. Conveniently located within walking distance to schools, IMS, and the great shops and restaurants on Main Street. Discover the charm of this neighborhood, where community spirit thrives, and friendly neighbors create a welcoming atmosphere. WELCOME HOME!
